Package by.bsuir.mycoolsite.service.factory

Class ServiceFactory

java.lang.Object
by.bsuir.mycoolsite.service.factory.ServiceFactory
public final class ServiceFactory extends Object
Factory class for obtaining service instances. This class follows the Singleton pattern with a single instance accessible via getInstance().
